             'phpDocString' => '/**
     * Return an entry name unique within the archive. On the first use the name
     * is returned unchanged; on a collision a counter is appended before the
     * file extension (e.g. "photo.jpg" -> "photo-2.jpg" -> "photo-3.jpg").
